Its somewhat under-powered and I don't love the aesthetics, especially after the 2nd generation facelift. I love the first generation tacomas but I had trouble finding one that wasn't destroyed. I also didn't want to deal with the potential reliability issues of a 15-20 year old vehicle. Now my brother is getting a 2004 trd off road with low mileage and I'm incredibly jealous. In the past I'd also thought about trading my single cab for a 2nd gen v6 with a double cab and extended bed. Should I just keep my truck until it dies?
